<p>
<A HREF="http://www.mckinley.com/" target=guide>Magellan Internet Guide</A> 
Magellan 
is an online guide to the Internet that includes original editorial content, a directory of rated and reviewed Internet sites,  a vast database of yet-to-be-reviewed
sites, Magellan includes Web sites, FTP and gopher servers, newsgroups, and Telnet sessions.
<P> You may Search Maggellan here 
