<P>
<A HREF= "http://webcrawler.com/" target=guide>WebCrawler</A> Today, the 
WebCrawler 
is a widely used search tool on the Internet: it is used by over
2 million people each week, who on average make more than three million queries per day. As part of America Online's<A HREF="http://gnn.com/"> GNN service</A>, WebCrawler continues to evolve and improve. 
<P>
<HR>
<P>
<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/" target=guide>Yahoo!</A>  A hierarchical 
subject-oriented guide for the World Wide Web and Internet. Yahoo! lists
sites and categorizes them into appropriate subject categories. 
