<h2>Advertising with SERVDirect</H2>

<FONT SIZE=4>When you advertise on the Internet with <B><I>SERVDirect,</I></B> your business ad is accessible 24 hours a day, 365 days a year on the World Wide Web. We are currently listing with popular search engines such as <EM><B> ALTA VISTA, LYCOS, an


d YAHOO.</B></EM>  We will continually update our links to the major Internet Search Engines.  We offer quality service at low prices.  Our services are customized to meet the needs of our clients.</FONT>  
<p>

