<P><H2>Directory Services</H2><UL><FONT SIZE=4>
<LI><B>Basic Listing</B> - 3 lines in our directory which may include:  Company Name &amp Logo, Address, Phone &amp Fax, email address,and brief slogan or description of your business under the category of your choice.  If the category you prefer is not l


isted, we will add it for you.  We will also link to your homepage or email address at no extra charge.  <A HREF="#price">Price Guide</A>
