 <LI><B>Deluxe Listing - </B>Includes the<B> Basic Listing with Coupon</B> as explained above, which will link to a full page ad custom designed specifically for your business.  This page may include your company logo or other materials you provide such a


s brochure information, pictures, map, coupon,  etc.. (Does not include graphics designed by SERVDirect) <A HREF="#price">Price Guide</A></UL>
