disk which we provide.  Please call or write for further information on this service.<A HREF="#other">Price Guide</A>
<P>
<LI><FONT SIZE=4><B>Image Scan Service</B> - We will scan your images to a 3 1/2" disk which we provide, or we will place them on your FTP Site.  All scanned material will be returned by mail with your disk.  Please specify Mac or PC Format.  SERVDirect c


annot be held responsible for any items lost or damaged during transport. <A HREF="#other">Price Guide</A>
