<a href="http://www.lib.virginia.edu/dic/African.html">African Art</a>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.vol.it/mirror/dali/"> Salvador Dali</A> (1904-89) One of Spain's most famous painters, he is considered the finest surrealist artist.
<P>
<A HREF="http://pharmdec.wustl.edu/juju/surr/surrealism.html"> !Surralisme!</A> The Surrealism Server 
<P>
<A HREF=" http://jefferson.village.virginia.edu/rossetti/rossetti.html">Dante Gabriel Rossetti</A> (1828-82)The Complete Writings and Pictures of
Dante Gabriel Rossetti: A Hypermedia
Research Archive. The English painter, poet and refined esthete who founded the Pre-Raphaelite artistic group.
