<p>
<A href="gopher://wiretap.spies.com/11/Gov/World">Constitutions of Countries from all over the world</a>
<P>
<A href="http://www.fedworld.gov/"> FedWorld Information Network</A>    The National Technical Information Service (NTIS)  accessing U.S. Government Information online. 
<p>
<A href="http://lcweb.loc.gov"> The Library of Congress</A>
<p>
<A href="gopher://wiretap.Spies.COM:70/11/Gov/US-History">US Historical Documents</A> A collection of Historical documents from US history
