<P>
<A HREF="http://www.libertynet.org/~lion/lion.html">LIbrary Information online network LION</A> An information resource for K-12 school librarians. sponsored by the Division of Libraries of the School District of Philadelphia as an information resource fo


r school librarians in Philadelphia and throughout the nation. 
<p>
<A
HREF="http://www.loc.gov/">Library of Congress</A> Search by the state or province you are interested in, or browse a list of schools in United States or Canada arranged by state or province. 
<p>
<A
HREF="http://witloof.sjsu.edu/peo/library.schools.html">Library Schools in the United States and Canada</A>
<p>
