HREF="http://sjcpl.lib.in.us/homepage/PublicLibraries/
PublicLibraryServers.html">SJCPL's List of Public Libraries with
Internet Services</A> Public Libraries on the Internet
<p>
<A HREF="http://www.state.wi.us/0/agencies/dpi/www/statelib.html">The State Library Gopher and Web Listing</A> Contains listing of state libraries that have gophers and/or Web pages.
