  <body><IMG ALIGN="left" SRC="bohr.gif">
    <center>
      <FONT SIZE="6">Welcome to Mr. Bohr's Help 
Page</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="4">Mr. Bohr is a good friend of Einstein and loves Math, 
Science and Biology.  Use the form below to send Mr. Bohr your 
questions about these subjects, or check out <A HREF="math_answers.html">Mr. 
Bohr's Answer Page</A>.<P>
    <form method=POST action="/cgi-sdirect/usr-bohr.cgi">
      Your Name:<input type=text name=realname size=30><br>
      E-Mail: <input type=text name=username size=40><br>
      City: <input type=text name=city size=15>, State: <input type=text name=state size=2> Country: <input type=text name=country size=15><p>
      
Please provide as many details as possible:<br>
      <textarea name=comments value=Math Question COLS=60
ROWS=17 wrap="soft"></textarea><p>
      <input type=submit value="Send My Question to Mr. Bohr"> or <input 
type=reset value="Erase and Start Over">
    </form><BR>It may take a day or two for a response. Mr. Bohr will 
answer your question as soon as he can.  He's always busy working on new 
theories!<BR>
    <hr>
<a href="http://sdirect.com/einstein/math_answers.html">Go to Mr. Bohr's 
Answer Page</a><br><P>
