<B>

<FONT SIZE=4> Here are some great sites you may want to check out. If you know a great teen site <a href="mailto:einstein@sdirect.com">email</a> us the web address and we will list it here.
<p>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="bludbr.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.myfuture.com/">It's My Future</A> Focus on teens, career and college information. Build a resume online, find out about college finance options, roomate stories, the military as an option and more. 
<P>
<A HREF="http://american.recordings.com/wwwofmusic/ubl/ubl.shtml"> The Ultimate Band List</A> The web's largest interactive list of music links where you the visitor can add the latest music links for your favorite bands. Find your favorite singer or band
s home page with this site.
<P>
<a href="http://www.ratw.com/">Rock Around The World</a>

<P>
<a href=http://members.tripod.com/~AmyDo/Index.htm> POPCORN</a> A cool Interactive Movie Database. This Web Site contains Movie Reviews designed for teenagers and children. 
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.cyberramp.net/~treptech/>The Outer Limits</A> A page created by teenagers for teenagers.
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.student.net">Student Net (college students zine)</A>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.mtlake.com/cyberteens/">Cyberteens</A> For teenagers by teenagers incluedes art, writings, puzzles and games
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.jayi.com/Fishnet/Edge/">Edge</A> An electronic news magazine by and for teens
<P>
<A HREF="http://www2.phillynews.com/online/fresh/">Fresh Ink</A> Issues and advice to teens on various topics from Philadelphia Online. 
<p>
<A HREF="http://www.pacificnews.org/yo/">YO! (Youth Outlook)</A>
<p>
<A HREF="http://www.wilmington.net/yi/">Young Images (Cape Fear)</A>  An online zine written by teens
<p>
<A HREF="http://www.iit.edu/~livewire/">Street Level Youth Media</A>
<p>
<A HREF="http://www2.nando.net/links/nandonext/next.html">NandoNext for Teens</A>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.islandnet.com/~luree/howto.html">How to Contact a Celebrity</A>
<p>
<A HREF="http://weber.u.washington.edu/~doit/Press/press.html">Disabled Teen Resources</A>
</B>
