<p>
Jules Verne
<BR>
<a href="http://www.datatext.co.uk/library/verne/world/chapters.htm">Around the World in Eighty Days</a>
<p><a href="http://etext.lib.virginia.edu/cgibin/toccer?id=VerTwen&tag=public&images=images/modeng&data=/lv1/Archive/eng-parsed&part=0">Twenty Thousand Leagues Under the Sea</a>
<p>
H.G. Wells
<BR>
<a href="http://www.fourmilab.ch/etexts/www/warworlds/warw.html">The War of the Worlds</a>
<p>
Oscar Wilde
<BR>
<a href="http://www.bibliomania.com/Fiction/wilde/stories/index.html"> Index of Short Stories &amp Poems in Prose by Oscar Wilde
<P>
Herman Melville<BR>
<A HREF = "gopher://wiretap.spies.com/00/Library/Classic/mobydick.txt">
Moby Dick</a>
<P>
<a href="gopher://lib.nmsu.edu:70/11/.subjects/Education/.childlit/.childbooks">Electronic Children's Books</a> Online children's classics
<P>
