Fairy tales and fables</a> Grimm's Fairy tales
<p>
<A HREF="http://www.fln.vcu.edu/Grimm/frog.html"> The Frog King</A>
<P>
<a href="http://etext.lib.virginia.edu/cgibin/toccer?id=AesFabl&tag=public&images=images/modeng&data=/lv1/Archive/eng-parsed&part=0">Aesop's Fables</a>
<P>
