 <CENTER> Knock! Knock!<FONT COLOR=MAGENTA> Who's there? <FONT COLOR=WHITE> Oh!  Hello there!</CENTER> <BR> <FONT COLOR=ORANGE> W<FONT SIZE=4>elcome to  the Riddle and Joke Page here at Einstein's Chalkboard. I am very busy these days putting up all the r
iddles and jokes that you send to us. How busy am I ? <FONT 
COLOR=YELLOW>(Hee-hee-hee)<FONT COLOR=ORANGE> Well, I'm never too busy for one more!  So <a href="email.html">email Einstein's Chalkboard</a> your favorite jokes and riddles and we will put them h
ere too!
