<FONT SIZE="4">T</FONT>HIS IS THE MISSION OF <FONT SIZE="4">R</FONT>OBLES &amp; <FONT SIZE="4">G</FONT>ONZALEZ, P.A.<BR>

<H5><FONT SIZE="4">P</FONT>ROTECTING THE RIGHTS OF INDIVIDUALS,<BR>
AND ENSURING THE SAFETY AND SECURITY OF THEIR<BR>
HOME, WORK, AND TRAVEL ENVIRONMENTS.<BR><BR>



<FONT SIZE="4">C</FONT>ORRECTING INJUSTICES, AND SEEING THAT THE<BR>
INJURED AND VICTIMIZED ARE PROPERLY COMPENSATED<BR>
IN A FAIR AND TIMELY MANNER.<BR><BR>



<FONT SIZE="4">P</FONT>ROVIDING A CLIMATE WHICH FOSTERS THE HIGHEST
STANDARDS<BR>
OF PROFESSIONALISM AND ETHICS FOR ALL MEMBERS OF THE FIRM.<BR>

