<td valign=top width=330>

<!-- <P><A HREF="inthenew.html"><H5><font size="5">I</font>N <font size="5">T</font>HE <font size="5">N</font>EWS</A> -->
<B>


<P><A HREF="toxic.html"><font size="5">T</font>OXIC <font size="5">T</font>ORT</A>
<P><A HREF="product.html"><font size="5">P</font>RODUCT <font size="5">L</font>IABILITY</A>
<P><A HREF="personal.html"><font size="5">P</font>ERSONAL <font size="5">I</font>NJURY</A>
<P><A HREF="construc.html"><font size="5">F</font>AULTY <font size="5">C</font>ONSTRUCTION</A>
<P><A HREF="commerce.html"><font size="5">C</font>OMMERCIAL <font size="5">L</font>ITIGATION</A>
<P><A HREF="about.html"><font size="5">A</font>BOUT <font size="5">T</font>HE <font size="5">F</font>IRM</A>
<P><A HREF="ttindex.html"><font size="5">T</font>RIAL <font size="5">T</font>IPS </A>
<P><A HREF="hbindex.html"><font size="5">A</font>DVANCED <font size="5">T</font>RIAL <font size="5">H</font>ANDBOOK</A>
<P><A HREF="newsolo.html"><font size="5">T</font>IPS <font size="5">F</font>OR <font size="5">G</font>OING <font size="5">S</font>OLO</A>
</B>
</H5>

<td valign=top width=600>
<STRONG><font size="4">A</font>s the world has grown more complex, so have the issues of liability and responsibility.

<P><font size="4">F</font>rom the fields and factories where workers toil, to the supermarkets and stores where the products of those labors are finally sold, the actions and activities of one community have become more interdependent with those of another. Consequently, our lives have become subject to forces which are often difficult to detect... or to comprehend.

<P><font size="4">I</font>n such an environment, the potential for corporate negligence and wrongdoing is very real. For many companies, the temptation is too great to resist. For individuals, the stakes are too high to ignore. <font size="4">R</font>obles &amp; <font size="4">G</font>onzalez is commited to correcting the injustices that occur when the negligence  and misbehavior of companies, individuals, and municipalities leads to harmful consequences for individuals, groups, or even entire communities.

</STRONG>

</table>



<A HREF="index.html"><P><IMG SRC="./images/backhome.gif" border="0" width="173" height="20" hspace="10"></A>
<A HREF="contact.html"><IMG SRC="./images/contact.gif" border="0" width="173" height="20" hspace="10"></A>
