<P><font size="4">M</font>any times, the suffering that results is compounded by the fact that the accident could have been avoided -- if only the proper precautions had been followed to ensure safety. When this happens, the legal system provides the means for accident victims to receive compensation for their suffering.

<P><font size="4">O</font>ver the years, <font size="4">R</font>obles &amp; <font size="4">G</font>onzalez has represented numerous clients in personal injury cases ranging from auto accidents to workplace safety issues to railroad disasters involving entire communities. The attorneys at <font size="4">R</font>obles &amp; <font size="4">G</font>onzalez have honed their personal injury skills through years of experience in local, state, and federal courts, and Ervin Gonzalez has been board certified as a specialist in civil trial law by the Florida Bar and the National Board for Trial Advocacy.
