<P><font size="4">I</font>n commercial ventures, disputes between individuals and/or companies can cause substantial losses and even break up thriving enterprises. If key employees or product/service providers are somehow negligent or do not live up to their contractual agreements, litigation can often be the only means to adequately resolve the matter and ensure that justice and fairness prevail.

<P><font size="4">R</font>obles &amp; <font size="4">G</font>onzalez provides sophisticated, high-caliber legal counsel and representation in commercial disputes. The firm's partners and associates are highly experienced attorneys in all areas of business torts, including cases involving breach of contract, civil theft, employer/employee conflicts, and negligent or fraudulent business practices.
