<TITLE>
Advanced Trial Handbook Index
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="./images/cbs.gif" text="#000000" link="#f00000" >
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="./images/rglogo.gif" width="606" height="105">

<H1>Advanced Trial Handbook</H1>


<H3>Helpful "Trial Tips" to Hone Your Litigation Skills</H3>


