<html>
<head><title>Royal Navy: Latest News</title>

</head>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"  
text="#000000">

<H2>Latest News</H2>
<HR>
<A HREF="archive/archive.htm" TARGET="contents"> News Archive</A>&#160;&#128;&#160;<A HREF="navynews.htm" TARGET="contents"> Navy News</A>
<HR></P>


<A HREF="latest/191296.htm" TARGET="contents"> <b>
OCEAN WAVE 97 - ROYAL NAVY TO THE ASIA PACIFIC REGION</B></A><BR>
A Royal Navy Task Group will be deploying to the Asia Pacific region during
1997. Led by the aircraft carrier HMS Illustrious, it will comprise some 20
surface ships, submarines and support vessels.</P>


<A HREF="latest/091.htm" TARGET="contents"> <b>COMMERCIAL PARTNER FOR NAVAL TRAINING</b></A><BR>
A commercial partnering scheme between the Royal Navy and the Flagship Training consortium has been given the go-ahead, Minister of State for the Armed Forces Nicholas Soames announced today.</P>

<A HREF="latest/130.htm" TARGET="contents"> <B>SEA HARRIER FA2 FIRST IN SERVICE FIRING OF AMRAAM</B></A><BR>
The Royal Navy carried out the first in service firing of the new Advanced Medium Range Air to Air Missile (AMRAAM) from the latest version of the Sea Harrier, the FA2.  </P>




<A HREF="latest/300496.htm" TARGET="contents"> <B>ARRIVAL OF NEW ADMIRAL MARKS CULMINATION OF CHANGES AT BASE</B></A><BR>

The last of the major changes at <A HREF="../../uk/clyde.htm" TARGET="contents"> HMNB Clyde</A> took place today (Tue 30 Apr) with the arrival of the new Flag Officer for Scotland, Northern England and Northern Ireland (FOSNNI) and Naval Base Commander, Clyde.</p>




</P>
<P>
<center>
<HR WIDTH="50%">



<A TARGET="_parent" HREF="../index.htm">Home Page</A>





