<head><title>Royal Navy: Worldwide: UK Portland </title>

</head>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"  
text="#000000">



<A HREF="britain.htm" TARGET="contents"> <H4>United Kingdom</A> &#160;&#128;&#160; <A HREF="../today/bases.htm" TARGET="contents"> Naval Bases</H4></A>

<H4>Royal Naval Air Station Portland</H4>


HMS OSPREY<BR>

Dorset<BR>

RNAS Portland has 306 acres of airfield, living accommodation, ranges and minor real estate.  </P>

With an annual budget of some &#163;45M, and 1400 service and civilian personnel, Portland is the Typed Air Station and main shore operating base for RN Lynx, with 60 aircraft in support of destroyers and frigates of the Fleet.</P>

		<table border=2>
<tr align=top><td> <B>AIRCRAFT</B>	</TD><TD>				<B>SQUADRON</B> </TD> </TR>

<tr align=top><td>		Lynx HAS 3	</TD><TD>				702 </TD> </TR>
	<tr align=top><td>	         HAS 3/8 </TD><TD>					815 </TD> </TR> </TABLE>


</P>
<P>
