<HEAD>
<TITLE>Executive Report Online: Help</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<a href="http://www.pittsburgh.net/cgi-bin/imagemap/ERBanner">
<IMG BORDER=0 ALIGN=bottom SRC="../pictures/Help.gif" ISMAP></a>
<p>
Welcome to Executive Report Online. <B>With ER Online, you can:</B>
<p>
<UL>
<LI>Find out what's happening in the Western Pennsylvania business community, <br>this month and every month. To see this month's issue, <A HREF="../zine/Current.Contents.html">click here</A>.
<LI>Research past issues of Executive Report Online in our <A HREF="../zine/Archives.html">Archives</A>.
<LI>Search for keywords by clicking on the <A HREF=../search/wais.cgi>SEARCH</a> button at the top of <br>every Executive Report Online page.
<LI><a href=Subscription.cgi>Order a subscription</a> to our print magazine.
</UL>

<B>Button Guide:</B>
<UL>
<LI><B>Home:</B> takes you to <B>HomePage</B> from anywhere in the site
<LI><B>Contents:</B> takes you to <B>Table of Contents</B> of current month's issue if you are not inside an issue; If you are looking at an issue, this button will take you to the <B>Table of Contents of Issue Being Reviewed</B>
<LI><B>Archives:</B> takes you to <B>Older Issues</B> from anywhere in the site
<LI><B>Search:</B> takes you to the screen which allows you to <B>Search All Issues</B>
<LI><B>Help:</B> brings you here
<LI><B>Current Issue:</B> takes you to <B>Table of Contents</B> of current month's issue

</UL>
<hr>
<ADDRESS><h5>&#169  Copyright 1994: Executive Report Inc. </ADDRESS>
</BODY>
