<TITLE>Executive Report Online</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<a href="http://www.pittsburgh.net/cgi-bin/imagemap/ERBanner">
<IMG BORDER=0 ALIGN=bottom SRC="../pictures/About.gif" ISMAP></a>
<p>
Welcome to Executive Report Online, the forum for Pittsburgh's business <br>
community. ER Online is a source of information and a vehicle for discussion <br>
among business people, both regionally and internationally. <p>

Through ER Online you can <p>

<UL>
<LI>Find out what's happening in the Western Pennsylvania business community, <br>this month and every month. To see this month's issue, <A HREF="../zine/Current.Contents.html">click here</A>.
<LI>Research past issues of Executive Report Online in our <A HREF="../zine/Archives.html">Archives</A>.
<LI>Search for keywords by clicking on the <A HREF=../search/wais.cgi>SEARCH</a> button at the top of <br>every Executive Report Online page.
<LI><a href=Subscription.cgi>Order a subscription</a> to our print magazine.
</UL>
<p>
If you need help at any time, click on the HELP button at the top
of every Executive Report Online page. <p>
<p>
You can go back to the first page ("home page") of Executive Report Online at any time by clicking on the HOME button on the top of every page.
<p>

<font size =+2><b>How to Reach Us </b></font size> <br>
To reach our advertising, circulation, or editorial offices:
<UL>
<LI>Call us at (412) 471-4585
<LI>Email feedback at <a href="feedback-form.html">er_editor@execreport.com</a>; 
<LI>Mail us at Riverview Publications Inc., 401 Liberty Avenue, 3 Gateway Center, 5th Floor, Pittsburgh, PA 15222-1004, USA.
</UL>
Executive Report welcomes your calls.
<p>

<font size =+2><b>Please Give Us Your Feedback Now</b></font size> <br>
We appreciate receving feedback from you. If you have comments, or suggestions for improving our magazine, or you just want to say hello, <a href = "feedback-form.html"> Click here </a> now.
<p>

<font size =+2><b>Publication Information</b></font size> <br>
Executive Report (ISSN 0279-1382) is published 12 times a year by Riverview Publications Inc., 401 Liberty Avenue, 3 Gateway Center, 5th Floor, Pittsburgh, PA 15222-1004.

<p>
<font size =+2><b>Readership and Circulation</b></font size> <br>
We have an audited circulation of 27,062 and a total readership of 93,000+. Top and middle managers make up 90% of our readers, with 44% owning their company or holding positions of partner. Our magazine is distributed primarily in twelve counties covering the western one-third of Pennsylvania, but it also covers parts of Ohio and West Virginia and the remaining portions of Pennsylvania.
<p>
<font size =+2><b>Copyright</b></font size> <br>
All contents of this publication are copyrighted by Riverview Publications Inc. All rigths reserved. Authorization to photocopy items for internal personal use, or the internal or personal use of specific clients, is granted by Executive Report, provided that a $2.50 fee is paid to Copyright Clearance Center Inc. 222 Rosewood Driver, Danvers, MA 01923; Tel: (508) 750-8400.
